name: My Kid Shuttle
overview: My Kid Shuttle provides a much needed student transportation service when parents cannot transport their children, and does so in an efficient and safe way. This company will also help you start your own kid shuttle company to you by allowing you to purchase their license agreement, which transfers their intellectual property to you in either an exclusive or non-exclusive license. You will receive their business plan, financials that are made based on your own pricing structure, standard operating procedures, marketing plan and all examples, human resources material, routing documents, examples and samples of all forms and documents. They also provide their insurance brokers information, auto broker, lists of equipment used and how to purchase, all formulas needed for cost analysis, web developer and consulting.
